Gold Declines 0.2% to $1,409.53 an Ounce in London, Erasing Earlier Climb

-- B y   N i c h o l a s   L a r k i n
-- 
2011-03-11T09:53:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-11/gold-declines-0-2-to-1-409-53-an-ounce-in-london-erasing-earlier-climb.html
Gold for immediate delivery
declined 0.2 percent to $1,409.53 an ounce at 9:52 a.m. in  London . The metal earlier today gained as much as 0.5 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
